content.rendered:
Directed by Divyang Thakkar

Written by Anckur Chaudhry. Divyang Thakkar

Cast Ranveer Singh (Jayesh). Shalini Pandey (Mudra). Boman Irani (Pruthvish). Ratna Pathak Shah (Jashoda). Puneet Issar (Amar Tau). Jia Vaidya (Siddhi). Deeksha Joshi (Preeti). Abhinay Raj Singh (Jayesh childhood)

Language Hindi

Producers Padam Bhushan. Maneesh Sharma

Production Yash Raj Films
